{"tid":1070690,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"世一魔獲評世界最佳運動員 力壓祖高域+費達拿當選","createTime":"2019-03-21T00:16:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T02:08:17.000Z","uid":94771,"like":5,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a06fe3f881d7673cab377bd0512e96aea48f24a1","tid":1070690,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T00:16:14.000Z","msg":"香港時間3月21日消息，在國際體育記者協會（AIPS）進行的投票，皇馬中場摩迪力壓兩大網球名將費達拿和祖高域，當選2018年度世界最佳男運動員。<br />\n<br />\n  該獎項由87個國家的359名體育記者投票選出，摩迪得到了419分，祖高域得到337分，費達拿得到290分。摩迪在2018年拿到了金球獎、世界足球先生、世界盃金球獎、歐洲足協最佳球員等一系列大將，如今他的榮譽室中又多了一個獎盃。<br />\n<br />\n  在最佳女運動員的評選中，美國體操名將拜爾斯得到427分，擊敗了捷克滑雪名將萊德卡和羅馬尼亞網球名將賀拿普當選。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2019/03/21/d/d9392dd972c5d83e2c3debcd8d9d1ebd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2019%2F03%2F21%2Fd%2Fd9392dd972c5d83e2c3debcd8d9d1ebd.jpg&h=a22a89cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n來源新浪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又一個世一"},{"pid":"3764f642f710be6a23201e12793a482e80f9ef61","tid":1070690,"uid":25345,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T00:18:26.000Z","msg":"佢面唔面孔,尷唔尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9311e67487dd6b1ed8011133771a44b8b7b71dd7","tid":1070690,"uid":90515,"like":7,"dislike":6,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T00:21:37.000Z","msg":"我宣佈世界大戰正式開始！<br />\n<br />\n新祖迷VS真皇迷<br />\n<br />\n參賽選手請於下方留言確認進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nHa Ha Madrid<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"febe4c170b529ee12747543892fb5321503d7e04","tid":1070690,"uid":32722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T00:25:29.000Z","msg":"佐真奴排第幾"},{"pid":"316b2e92485cac68c36c676c8e5f081d8a46b03b","tid":1070690,"uid":155902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T00:33:42.000Z","m